race.comment: BLACK NATURE (8) made it two on the bounce here last start when arriving just in time over this trip. Is drawn to advantage and Nock's booking signals confidence. Hat-trick inbound. GLOWING RAPIDS (2) will cross quickly from the wide alley to give supporters a bold sight. Boyd's claim helps under the big weight and he will prove tough to reel in if left alone in front. CHESTIME (14) is desperate to land the killer blow. Is 1/1 at this venue and has an affinity for this distance. Don't take lightly. STOCKHOLM (12) is building nicely, though will be tested by the draw. Keeping safe for a minor spot.
